OL,4,Cgrieving relatives paying for funerals
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA funeral worker from Devon who went
OL,8,Fon the run after defrauding grieving
OL,9,Frelatives who thought they were paying
OL,10,Ffor funerals out of more than #9,000
OL,11,Fhas been jailed for almost two years.
OL,13,FSteven Drinkwater, 47, from Ottery St
OL,14,FMary in Devon, pleaded guilty to eight
OL,15,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,16,Frepresentation.
