OL,3,C'Callous' fraudster who tricked
OL,4,Cgrieving relatives paying for funerals
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FVictims included a mother with a
OL,8,Fstillborn daughter, bereaved spouses,
OL,9,Fand other parents who had lost
OL,10,Fchildren, according to the Crown
OL,11,FProsecution Service (CPS).
OL,13,FDrinkwater was jailed on Wednesday 7
OL,14,FFebruary for 20 months at
OL,15,FWolverhampton Crown Court.
OL,17,FBetween 2015 and 2016, Steven
OL,18,FDrinkwater worked for a funeral
OL,19,Fdirector.
