OL,3,C'Callous' fraudster who tricked
OL,4,Cgrieving relatives paying for funerals
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FFor a year he persuaded families to
OL,8,Fpay cash for funerals so that he could
OL,9,Fpocket the money.
OL,11,FIn June 2015, a staff member overheard
OL,12,FDrinkwater accepting a sale for a
OL,13,Ffuneral package and witnessed cash
OL,14,Fbeing given to him.
OL,16,FWhen asked if he had accepted a sale,
OL,17,FDrinkwater said he hadn't.
OL,19,FBut the staff member further probed
OL,20,Fhim and he eventually admitted to the
OL,21,Fsale.
