OL,7,FAn investigation was launched and a
OL,8,Fpolice appeal was issued. He remained
OL,9,Fwanted until his arrest on 7 January
OL,10,F2024 after he was detained by police
OL,11,Fin Devon following a tipoff.
OL,13,FThe 46-year-old pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Feight counts of fraud and was
OL,15,Fsentenced to serve 10 months behind
OL,16,Fbars and a further 10 months on
OL,17,Flicence.
OL,19,FAny further offending in this period
OL,20,Fwill mean he will return immediately
OL,21,Fto prison.
