OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Isobel Griffiths,
OL,8,Ffrom Wolverhampton Police, said: "This
OL,9,Fwas an awful crime in which Drinkwater
OL,10,Fcallously targeted grieving families
OL,11,Fwhen they were at their most
OL,12,Fvulnerable.
OL,14,F"He then went on the run, hoping to
OL,15,Fnever have to face up to his crimes.
