OL,7,F"The company that Drinkwater worked
OL,8,Ffor are also victims in this. They
OL,9,Ftrusted him to take care of these
OL,10,Fgrieving families and instead he took
OL,11,Fadvantage. The company honoured all
OL,12,Fsales that Drinkwater dealt with to
OL,13,Fensure no family was at a loss.
OL,15,F"The sentence today shows that we will
OL,16,Fnever give up in getting justice for
OL,17,Fvictims of crime."
